COLD SDS and disconnect the Service jumper.
</p></li><li id="LI_21C8B271522344C0958B457D5D3BA087" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the left hand winder cover. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA058" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-018F073E-4ED3-414A-8FEC-3740B53F5DBE.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 24 How to remove the left (or right) hand side cover of the winder?>24 How to remove the left (or right) hand side cover of the winder</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the take-up media shaft. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="19DISA015" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-2885BF56-7B36-423E-B567-AB29516FD4CC.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 19 How to remove the take-up media shaft?>19 How to remove the take-up media shaft</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the left hand winder drive assembly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
