</p></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_A32A562039FB485780CA65B069EE577C" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_1D9EE245DE6547E09D8CB22E45CFC7A0" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T10. 
</p></li><li id="LI_55373F9DAE644089ABBC568E03CDE4FC" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-1C6A5506-8461-4BFD-8B7C-FB47C7EF289A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0568BF02-E45C-42FC-902A-D449A1BCF9EC-low.png" id="IMAGE_1EE8E6CF131C4064913FA3D3B4E13E44" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0568BF02-E45C-42FC-902A-D449A1BCF9EC-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_58DD54200DF045D585CD5AD03B1E0207" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_1B54D75E6F9946209396D6FC85A16BBB" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Locate the motor on the bracket. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the sensor connector. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-4E440938-4EF7-43BA-9432-5FC605A4407C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-03C70ABD-38BE-4687-A03D-5AA44160D72A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-03C70ABD-38BE-4687-A03D-5AA44160D72A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Turn the assembly around. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the tension spring from the motor assembly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Loosen the 3 nuts on the motor assembly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Now you are able to unhook the drive belt. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-90C26DEE-99CC-4F62-BE93-B3F134CB904E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-9FB10E26-20B7-4D8C-B505-16D89AC8EEE9-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-9FB10E26-20B7-4D8C-B505-16D89AC8EEE9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Turn the assembly around. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the motor connector. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 4 T20 screws that hold the motor. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the motor. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-FF82B149-8E83-4177-BFF6-63A988482621" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-03C70ABD-38BE-4687-A03D-5AA44160D72A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-03C70ABD-38BE-4687-A03D-5AA44160D72A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_F77204E29D3E4F6D8F3503958683C72F" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Reconnect the Service jumper, exit SDS and press 'Restart' on the operator panel. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-8D3A1F62-9497-4853-8507-1AEACBF21ABC.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dis-assembly</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
